!.mcp.json.example
# Local bank statements (not committed — personal financial data)
# Anchored to repo root so it can't accidentally match source dirs of the same name.
/MainBankAccount/
# Exported data backups (not committed — personal financial data)
# Anchored to repo root so it does NOT match the backup-feature source dirs
# (src/.../Backup/). An unanchored `Backup/` would drop those on a fresh clone/init.
/Backup/
# Playwright MCP scratch artifacts (page snapshots, console logs, screenshots)
.playwright-mcp/
# Code-coverage run output + generated reports
CoverageRun/
CoverageReport/